[I] Utilities for the MATE Desktop Environment

[T] mate-utils contains MATE Utility programs for the MATE Desktop. mate-utils
[T] is a fork of GNOME Utilities.

[U] https://mate-desktop.org/

[A] MATE developer
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/desktop/mate

[L] GPL
[V] 1.28.1

[D] 0 mate-utils-1.28.1.tar.xz https://github.com/mate-desktop/mate-utils/releases/download/v1.28.1/

